gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 110, Rockets 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pelicans defeated the Rockets, 110-99. Jonas Valanciunas notched 25 points and 14 rebounds for the Pelicans, while Brandon Ingram added 24 points, 10 rebounds and four assists in the victory. Jalen Green tallied 31 points (5-12 3pt. FG), four rebounds, four assists and three steals for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Pelicans improve to 27-21 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 22-25.
